Citizens Who Care provides social support services to older adults and their family caregivers. These services are provided by trained, caring volunteers, with the support of our professional staff, in Yolo County and neighboring communities.

Programs include:
 * In-Home respite care
 * Convalescent Hospital Visitation
 * "Time Off for Caregivers"

Citizens Who Care also offers the very popular fundraising [http://www.dcn.davis.ca.us/go/care/Concert.html Winter Concert] at the ["Varsity Theatre"] each February.
